headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Business Discounts
content:
Those looking to take ride on the wild side can purchase an MC Clubhouse for 30% off market price.

Registered CEOs who own a Nightclub can fend off attacks from jealous enemies by enlisting a Security Upgrade at the velvet rope for 40% off this week.

Executives can also upgrade their Office Accommodations and add a bed for 30% off.
